Class ShortcutServletTransitionVisitor<K,T>

  • java.lang.Object

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Contexed, TransitionVisitor<T>

    public class ShortcutServletTransitionVisitor<K,T>
extends AbstractTransitionVisitor<K,T>
    A cut-down version of the ServletTransitionVisitor that generates those FormResults that can be generated without taking a lock, for example the redirect to the form jsp. Otherwise the visitor returns null.

    spb
